      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working on a design project and im a bit stuck on the physics side. can u explain how a cantilevered balcony stays stable? like, how does it not just tip over if there's no support at the outer edge? i know theres something about moment and torque involved but im not sure how they balance out.",
